# 🏥 Disease Prediction System  

## 📌 Overview  
This is a **Machine Learning-based Disease Prediction System** built using **Streamlit**. It predicts:  
- **Diabetes**  
- **Heart Disease**  
- **Parkinson's Disease**  

The system takes user inputs and uses **pre-trained ML models** to predict the likelihood of these diseases.

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used  
- **Python**  
- **Streamlit** (for the Web App)  
- **Scikit-Learn** (for ML models)  
- **Pandas & NumPy** (for data processing)  
- **Pickle** (for saving and loading trained models)

---

## 🔧 Installation Guide  
Copy and paste the following commands into your terminal:

### 1️⃣ Clone the Repository  
```sh
git clone https://github.com/Preethika1801/Prediction_of_DiseaseOutBreak.git  
cd Prediction_of_DiseaseOutBreak
```

### 2️⃣ Install Required Libraries  
```sh
pip install -r Req_libraries.txt
```

### 3️⃣ Run the Application  
```sh
streamlit run web.py
```

---

## 📂 Project Structure  
```
📁 Disease-Prediction-System/
│-- 📂 Datasets/  
│   ├── diabetes.csv          # Dataset for Diabetes  
│   ├── heart.csv             # Dataset for Heart Disease  
│   ├── parkinsons.csv        # Dataset for Parkinson’s
│-- 📂 Training_models/ 
│   ├── diabetes_model.ipynb 
│   ├── diabetes_model.sav    # Trained ML model for Diabetes  
|   ├── heart_model.ipynb
│   ├── heart_model.sav       # Trained ML model for Heart Disease
│   ├── parkinson.ipynb 
│   ├── parkinson.sav         # Trained ML model for Parkinson’s  
│-- 📄 web.py                 # Streamlit app script  
│-- 📄 Req_libraries.txt      # Required dependencies  
│-- 📄 README.md              # Project documentation    
```

---

## 🚀 Features  
✅ **User-friendly Interface** with Streamlit  
✅ **Real-time Predictions** using ML models  
✅ **Error Handling** for invalid inputs  
✅ **Pre-trained ML Models** for faster predictions  


